<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Bog Creatures Lab</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" media="screen" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.4/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <script src="//code.jquery.com/jquery.js"></script>
  <script src="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.4/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>


<div class="container">
  <div class="row">


    <div class="navbar-header">
      <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
        <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
    <div class="page-header">
        <h1>Bog Creatures</h1>
    </div>
      <ul class="nav nav-pills nav_bar">
        <li role="presentation" class="active"><%= link_to 'Home', '/' %></li>
        <li role="presentation"><%= link_to 'Creatures', creatures_path %></li>
        <li role="presentation"><%= link_to 'New Creature',new_creature_path %></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-6 col-md-8 col-offset-2">

      <div class="well">
        <p>When I think of Bog creatures, it makes me think of the Diablo game from Blizzard. Bog Creatures are Frog Demons which live in the jungles of Kehjistan. This amphibian beasts can be encountered usually near creeks, where they emerge and might take a careless hero by surprise. Bog Creatures have a harmless melee attack. However they shoot much more effective fire balls from distance that have a knockback effect. I have included a few of them. If you happen to know a few more, please make sure to add them to the list.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-8 col-md-8 col-lg-8">
      <%= yield %>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>